**AfterArtificial is an AI Product Platform that generates consumer and
enterprise software from a unified architecture.**

- Products are **Life Domain / Industry Domain modules**, not standalone apps.
- Every product uses `after_ecosystem`: After ID, After+, event bus,
  product APIs, shared calendar / notifications / search / documents /
  wallet / family / marketplace / settings / personalization.
- Publish domain events; subscribe to influence other modules ŌĆö do not
  hard-import sibling apps. Every domain can communicate with every other.
- Cross consumerŌåöenterprise calls go through `AfterSecureInteropBridge`
  with `interop.cross_line` scope.
- AfterAI must receive `AfterEcosystemAiContext` for cross-module awareness.
- Adding SuperKids / SuperFood / SuperMunicipality does not change the
  fabric architecture ŌĆö only a new top-layer module.
